## Fazer Chamada

POST http://<hostname or Ip>/app_dev.php/api/students/fouls
(header)
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization TOKEN56FRSE17739H97U9WU4HD702N3U
(body)
{
	"fouls": [
		{
			"student_id": 1,
			"classroom_id": 1,
			"date": "2016-09-12",
			"quantity": 4
		}
		{
			"student_id": 2,
			"classroom_id": 1,
			"date": "2016-09-12",
			"quantity": 4
		}
	]	
}

---------
{
  "type": "created",
  "title": "Operacao realizada com sucesso!",
  "statusCode": 201,
  "message": "Faltas marcadas com sucesso!",
  "extraInformation": {
	"students": [
		{
			"name": "Gabriel Sousa Kraszczuk",
			"registry": "135025-1",
			"status_code": 0,
			"fouls": {
				"subject": {
					"name": "Eletiva II",
	    				"abbreviation": "ELTII",
				},
				"quantity": 4,
				"date":"2016-12-24"
			}
		}
	]
}

